[Daniel 8:22](../../../bib/kjv/dan008.htm#022.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_022">dan 8:22</span></span>

four kingdoms

The four empires into which Alexander's empire was divided about B.C.
300; Greece, Asia Minor, including Syria, Egypt, the East.

[Daniel 8:23](../../../bib/kjv/dan008.htm#023.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_023">dan 8:23</span></span>

king of fierce countenance

That is, Antiochus Epiphanes who arose out of Syria, one of the "four
kingdoms," B.C. 170.

